{"tid":47025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有區議員問盧偉聰旺角騷亂為何不發橡膠子彈甚至開槍","createTime":"2016-12-20T05:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T14:39:02.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf501f867301f44b81dfd5b166d94a02512d312d","tid":47025,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰出席元朗區議會會議，簡述本港的罪案情況。有區議員反映區內警力不足，盧偉聰表示，會根據各區人口、罪案數字及交通等估計人手，又說每年均會檢討人手安排，如果有需要會於內部調配人員到相關警區。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰又說，警方十分關注非華裔人士的犯案趨勢，尤其是持行街紙的非華裔人士。他說有組織罪案及三合會調查科會統籌有關工作，分析情報並進行聯合行動。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有區議員認為警方處事欠強硬。區議員郭強質疑警方於年初的旺角騷亂事件，為何不發射橡膠子彈，甚至開槍擊斃示威者，盧偉聰表示，警方不會考慮示威者的政治團體，如果有違法行為便會作出執法行動，強調不會手軟或手硬。"},{"pid":"bbe4b05f8683ea958b5c3e99a4b63b72d1d72fcb","tid":47025,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b31eb0effeb21fd1622d833d6cad7653b544b3f","tid":47025,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"a66fa6b1493c18af859bd5d282526e65703f3e74","tid":47025,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"又係民建聯班賤畜"},{"pid":"3c528eb6d092b8b2ad42965cf07f415072e884f4","tid":47025,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"咪開撚左槍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要打死人先叫開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3154eac6f7292c467bab27001931f27002f06fd9","tid":47025,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"好多區議員都垃圾黎"},{"pid":"8d92d3337af22db69b4